OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been seriously injured in a
OL,7,Fstabbing in north Belfast in what has
OL,8,Fbeen described as a 'depraved
OL,9,Fbarbaric' attack.
OL,11,FOne MLA described it as "extreme
OL,12,Fbrutality".
OL,14,FSocial media footage of the incident
OL,15,Fhas been circulating online.
OL,17,FThe PSNI said officers were called to
OL,18,FKinnaird Avenue around 10.30pm on
OL,19,FMonday and the injured man was taken
OL,20,Fto hospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
