OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781032284
OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,FAnother man was arrested in connection
OL,7,Fwith the incident and taken into
OL,8,Fcustody.
OL,10,FOfficers remained at the scene on
OL,11,FTuesday morning.
OL,13,FAnyone who witnessed the incident or
OL,14,Fhas dashcam or CCTV footage has been
OL,15,Furged to contact police.
OL,17,FSinn Fein MP John Finucane condemned
OL,18,Fthe incident describing it as an
OL,19,F"appalling violent" attack.
OL,26,@yD@Grr
