OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781032284
OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,F"This is deeply shocking, there is no
OL,7,Fplace for violence of any kind in our
OL,8,Fcommunities," he said.
OL,10,F"My thoughts are with the victim and I
OL,11,Fhope they make a full recovery.
OL,13,F"I would urge anyone with information
OL,14,Fto come forward to the PSNI
OL,15,Fimmediately so a full investigation
OL,16,Fcan be carried out."
OL,18,FNorth Belfast MLA Nuala McAllister
OL,19,Fvoiced her condemnation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
