OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781032284
OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,F"I am horrified by the footage
OL,7,Femerging from north Belfast, depicting
OL,8,Fsome of the most depraved and barbaric
OL,9,Fviolence I have ever seen," she said.
OL,11,F"My thoughts are with the victim and
OL,12,Fall those who witnessed this deeply
OL,13,Fdisturbing incident. This extreme
OL,14,Fbrutality has no place whatsoever in
OL,15,Four society.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]sD@AOU
