PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1781032284
OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,F"The investigation must be allowed to
OL,7,Ftake its course. We must give the PSNI
OL,8,Fthe space and support they need to
OL,9,Festablish the full facts and ensure
OL,10,Fthat the individual responsible is
OL,11,Fheld to account. Our focus must remain
OL,12,Fon securing justice and ensuring that
OL,13,Fthose responsible face the full force
OL,14,Fof the law.
OL,16,F"I'd appeal to anyone with any
OL,17,Finformation that could help police to
OL,18,Fcontact them urgently to help them
OL,19,Fwith their investigation."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU{D@ZO]
