OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,FDUP councillor Jordan Doran said he
OL,7,Fwas "left shocked and deeply
OL,8,Fconcerned" by footage circulating
OL,9,Fonline following the stabbing.
OL,11,F"Many residents have contacted me
OL,12,Fexpressing concerns about community
OL,13,Fsafety and seeking reassurance
OL,14,Ffollowing this incident," he said.
OL,16,F"Those concerns are entirely
OL,17,Funderstandable. People deserve to feel
OL,18,Fsafe in their homes and communities,
OL,19,Fregardless of where they live."
OL,26,@oD@EOUpD@JO]sD@AOUvD@YO]xD@AOU{D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
