OL,3,C'Extreme brutality': Man seriously
OL,4,Cinjured in Belfast stabbing
OL,6,FHe continued: "What is beyond dispute
OL,7,Fis that violence of this nature has no
OL,8,Fplace in North Belfast.
OL,10,F"I will be engaging with the PSNI and
OL,11,Frelevant agencies as a matter of
OL,12,Furgency to ensure residents receive
OL,13,Fthe information and reassurance they
OL,14,Fdeserve."
